"'''The Queen of Air and Darkness'''" is the third adventure in the ''[[Dawn of Defiance]]'' campaign. It is written by [[Rodney Thompson]] and released on [[February 28]], [[2008]].

==Plot summary==
The players investigate [[Darga Jiramma Mionne|Darga the Hutt]] at the [[Cloud City Sabacc Tournament]] and confront him before they rush to stop [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces destroying a [[Tibanna gas hauler]].

